      "content": "thanks for those stats. i want to dig a bit deeper into the causality. while you mentioned systemic issues, some researchers argue that socioeconomic factors alone don't fully explain the gaps once you control for variables. do you have any information or studies that look into whether there are any biological or innate cultural differences that contribute to these different statistical outcomes?",
